# Wikipedia - Rabbit Hole Emulated mobile
Here we test the Wikipedia rabbit hole user journey. We first go the [main Wikipedia page](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Main_Page), 
then to the [Barack Obama page](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barack_Obama) and lastly the [Democratic party page](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Democratic_Party_(United_States)).
